        <h2 class="learn-footer-title">Why Neo‑Brutalism Feels So Powerful</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="learn-footer-right">
        <p class="learn-footer-sub">Because it breaks the rules.</p>
        <p>When a design ignores conventional harmony, our brains notice immediately. This creates:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Strong memorability</li>
          <li>Visual uniqueness</li>
          <li>Edginess</li>
          <li>Cultural resonance with Gen Z and experimental digital art</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Neo‑brutalism is visually confrontational on purpose.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
